# The bot itself (bot.py) needs NO keys — leave this file alone unless you
# want the optional "ask your data" tool (ask.py).
#
# ask.py uses the Claude API to answer questions about the collected comments.
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys (paid — pennies per question),
# then copy this file to ".env" and paste your key below.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# Optional: use a cheaper/faster model for answers (default is claude-opus-4-8).
# ASK_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5
